OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1782762496
OL,3,CFrance's record heatwave led to 1,000
OL,4,Cexcess deaths in days, officials say
OL,6,FFrance saw around 1,000 additional
OL,7,Fdeaths last week at the height of its
OL,8,Frecord-breaking heatwave, as extremely
OL,9,Fhigh temperatures shifted eastward
OL,10,Facross Europe.
OL,12,FFuneral directors were struggling to
OL,13,Ffind space for bodies in Paris's
OL,14,Foverwhelmed mortuaries as the nation
OL,15,Froasted above 40C for several days and
OL,16,Fexperienced severe thunderstorms.
OL,18,FDuring one that raged over the French
OL,19,Fcapital on Sunday, witnesses filmed
OL,20,Fthe iconic Eiffel Tower being struck
OL,21,Fby a bolt of lightning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
