PN,31403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1782762496
OL,3,CFrance's record heatwave led to 1,000
OL,4,Cexcess deaths in days, officials say
OL,6,FWorld Health Organisation director-
OL,7,Fgeneral Tedros Adhanom Ghebreyesus
OL,8,Fblamed climate change and global
OL,9,Fwarming for the "once-in-a-generation"
OL,10,Fheatwave, adding: "Europe is the
OL,11,Ffastest-warming continent on Earth,
OL,12,Fheating at twice the global average.
OL,14,F"Right now, 150 million people are
OL,15,Fliving under extreme heat, hundreds
OL,16,Fhave died, schools are shut, grids are
OL,17,Fbuckling."
OL,26,@yD@JO]
