OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1782762496
OL,3,CFrance's record heatwave led to 1,000
OL,4,Cexcess deaths in days, officials say
OL,6,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FIn Berlin, police used water cannons
OL,12,Fto cool down the crowds by spraying
OL,13,Fmist.
OL,15,FMore than 600 passengers had to be
OL,16,Fevacuated from an overheated train in
OL,17,FBrandenburg, and two hospitalised
OL,18,Fafter a tree fell onto an overhead
OL,19,Fpower line during a storm on Saturday
OL,20,Fevening.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
