CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1782762496
OL,3,CFrance's record heatwave led to 1,000
OL,4,Cexcess deaths in days, officials say
OL,6,FIn Sweden, several people were injured
OL,7,Fwhen they were hit by lightning at
OL,8,FTosselilla Sommarland amusement park,
OL,9,Fthe country's TT news agency reported.
OL,11,FOne Parisian funeral director,
OL,12,FZouhaeir Hertelli, says he receives
OL,13,Fhundreds of calls daily but has no
OL,14,Froom left.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
