PN,31407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1782762496
OL,3,CFrance's record heatwave led to 1,000
OL,4,Cexcess deaths in days, officials say
OL,6,FPublic Health France reports a surge
OL,7,Fin deaths, particularly among older
OL,8,Fpeople. Last week, deaths exceeded
OL,9,F1,200 on Wednesday and rose to over
OL,10,F1,400 on Thursday and Friday. The
OL,11,Fagency expects these numbers to rise
OL,12,Fas more death certificates are
OL,13,Fprocessed.
OL,15,F"We're facing a really catastrophic
OL,16,Fsituation," Hertelli said. "I'm
OL,17,Fgetting hundreds of calls.
OL,19,F"We're dealing with an enormous spike
OL,20,Fof deaths because of the heatwave and
OL,21,Fwe're really full, full, full."
